## Context

The file `src/pipelines.js` contains ~3500 lines. It defines pipeline classes, a `SUPPORTED_TASKS` mapping, and a `pipeline()` factory function. I need to add a new pipeline that accepts an image + text prompt and generates text output (e.g., "Describe this image in detail").

## Existing Patterns (from exploration)

### Imports (lines 20-45)
Model auto-classes are imported from `'./models.js'`. `AutoModelForImageTextToText` is already defined and exported in `src/models.js` (line 8736) but NOT yet imported in `src/pipelines.js`. It supports 11 models: LLaVA, Florence2, Qwen2-VL, Moondream, SmolVLM, PaliGemma, etc.

